OL,3,CUK transmitter network hit by
OL,4,Celectricity bill increase
OL,6,GIf your electricity bill has gone up
OL,7,Gin the last 12 months, spare a
OL,8,Gthought for Arqiva, the company
OL,9,Gbehind the transmitter masts that
OL,10,Gpower the UK's terrestrial TV and
OL,11,Gradio networks.
OL,13,FIt's previous fixed rate deal ended
OL,14,Fin March, resulting in a 230% hike in
OL,15,Fthe unit cost of power, according to
OL,16,Fthe company's latest financial report.
OL,18,FThe days of switching off
OL,19,Ftransmitters overnight to save
OL,20,Felectricity are long gone, with most
OL,21,Fchannels running services through the
OL,22,Fnight.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/5
